The six numbers surrounding any number n in this pattern are n-1, n+1, n-15, n-16, n+15, n+16 (this is a result of the hexagonal pattern). Therefore, the sum of the six numbers surrounding 2026 is 

2026-1 + 2026+1 + 2026-15 + 2026-16 + 2026+15 + 2026+16 = 6*2026 + (-1+1-15-16+15+16) = 12156.
